txt.en: 'Bah, that would have only been a scratch... Come again!'
'Let us see if I can give you another.'
'A most palpable hit! Try for another?'
'Truly, your heart holds no fear, brother.'
'Is there any word from the west?'
'No word yet. Our focus should remain on the east.'
'True, but my heart goes to those in Trestlebridge should the rumours turn out to be true.'
'Yes but if we fail to continue to turn the advance of the Orcs in the east, then Trestlebridge will fall.'
